{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f7088e292a","title":"与南京当局谈判之意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c77832bd7","index":0,"year":1936,"month":3,"day":4,"articleId":"f7088e292a"}],"tags":[{"id":"565c30a42f","name":"博古","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"76b2eec9b8","type":"paragraph","text":"与南京当局谈判之意见","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"f7088e292a"},{"id":"21aaaa840f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年3月4日）博古同志转剧继音兄：（甲）弟等十分欢迎南京当局的觉悟与明智的表示，为联合全国力量抗日救国，弟等愿意与南京当局开始具体实际之谈判（乙）我兄复命南京时，望息切提出弟等下列意见（一）停止一切内战，全国武装不分红白，一致抗日（二）组织国防政府与抗日联军；（三）容许全国主力红军迅速集中河北，首先抵御日寇迈进（四）释放政治犯，容许人民政治自由：（五）内政与经济上实行初步与必要的改革（丙）同意我兄即返回南京，以便迅速碰商大计","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"f7088e292a"},{"id":"692b4de0e8","type":"paragraph","text":"张毛彭","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"f7088e292a"},{"id":"bb16ded1b8","type":"paragraph","text":"四号十二时[1]这是毛泽东和洛雨（张同天）、彭德怀给博古（秦邦宪）转周继吾","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"f7088e292a"}],"page":{"id":"16812b6cc4","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"f7088e292a","start":302,"end":302}}}},"__N_SSG":true}